data.description: Find your dream home right here in Cypress Village. This custom 3 bed 3.5 bath Truland home is in a prime location; located across from Orange Beach Middle and High School! Step inside to be greeted with a spacious and sunlit floor plan with ample room for entertaining. 10' ceilings and 8' doors add an extra layer of elegance. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, all stainless appliances, and an island bar. The first floor master suite is complete with a luxurious en-suite bathroom complete with a soaking tub, separate shower, and double vanity, and walk-in closet. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms with their own private baths reside on the second floor. Cypress Village is home to an extraordinary community pool with a zero entry lazy river, mushroom fountain and more. The Wharf is a short ride on the golf cart (or walk), where you can find amazing entertainment, dining, and shopping! The white sand beaches of Orange Beach are only a few minutes away! This home offers luxury, convenience, and the perfect coastal lifestyle! Schedule your showing today and make it yours!
